    quote: "We're delighted to have reconnected with the Vogt Real Estate Group! Kris and Kellie are exceptionally joyful people and realtors. Our sale was smooth and efficient; we were treated with warmth, honesty and integrity. We'll recommend them to all of our friends and family!",
